@SG_FUNC static SGXString readAllText(const SGXString& filePath);
Reads all text in the file at $filePath and returns the text as a SGXString.
@SG_NOTE You are strongly encouraged to use binary files instead for better support and simplicity.
@SG_WARN If $filePath cannot be opened, this is undefined behaviour. There is no error handling.
@SG_FUNC static void writeAllText(const SGXString& filePath, const SGXString& contents);
Overwrite the contents of the file at $filePath with $contents.
@SG_NOTE You are strongly encouraged to use binary files instead for better support and simplicity.
@SG_WARN This irreversibly overwrites all data previously stored in the file.
@SG_WARN If $filePath cannot be opened, this is undefined behaviour. There is no error handling.
